graph TD
    Start([Start]) --> Validate[Validate Input]
    Validate --> Decision{Valid?}
    Decision -->|Yes| Process[Process Data]
    Decision -->|No| Error[Show Error]
    Error --> Validate
    Process --> Store[(Store Results)]

    subgraph Pipeline
      Process
      Store
    end

    Store --> Notify[Send Notification]
    Notify --> End([End])
